akke.", "- Hvis jeg var lastebilsj\u00e5f\u00f8r ville jeg ikke ha kj\u00f8rt ned den bakken slik den er n\u00e5. Det har v\u00e6rt s\u00e5kalt \u00abjo-jo-v\u00e6r\u00bb, med sludd, sn\u00f8 og regn om hverandre. Da b\u00f8r en sj\u00e5f\u00f8rs vurdering v\u00e6re \u00e5 holde seg unna slike bakker, sier han."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "796a5c44f34652685e8c39dc0b35c8962d234005435b20231ae5877aa576c007"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-02T00:12:31.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "I g\u00e5r fikk Asgeir Isdahl en lastebil i hagen. N\u00e5 \u00f8nsker naboene i \u00c5sbakken i Trondheim gjennomkj\u00f8ring forbudt p\u00e5 vinters tid."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/nyheter/trondheim/article13986514.ece/b57nww/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Lastebil%20i%20hagen20161228-HHJ-02"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/5e5d7c1119cd3ea9ee5849721ca3461f0f842f0a.jpg?5991f0fb"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Det er et sjansespill \u00e5 kj\u00f8re her -adressa.no", "Lastebil i hagen", "\u00d8nsker gjennomkj\u00f8ring forbudt", "Prioriterer \u00c5sbakken"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "5e5d7c1119cd3ea9ee5849721ca3461f0f842f0a"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "automotive"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["bratt bakke", "bil", "bakke", "gata", "trondheim", "gjennomkj\u00f8ring forbudt", "kj\u00f8re"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["bakkaunet", "\u00e5sbakken", 